snippet.title: Fresh Start | Console Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Travel the world and give it the Fresh Start it deserves! In this relaxing single player game, you embark on a mission to clean up the world and restore nature to its fresh and colourful shape. Watch as the world changes in front of your eyes as you help animals, solve puzzles and grow plants around you.

Pre-order physical copies now at Signature Edition Games!
Switch: https://signatureeditiongames.com/products/fresh-start-standard-edition-switch?variant=44105063432421
PS5: https://signatureeditiongames.com/products/fresh-start-standard-edition-playstation-5?variant=44105360474341
